{"id":"guide/i18n-overview","title":"Angular 国际化","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"angular-internationalization\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 国际化<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Angular Internationalization<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><em>国际</em>化，有时称为 i18n，是设计和准备项目，以便在世界各地的不同语言环境使用的过程。<em>本地化</em>是为不同的语言环境构建项目版本的过程。本地化过程包括以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><em>Internationalization</em>, sometimes referenced as i18n, is the process of designing and preparing your project for use in different locales around the world.\n<em>Localization</em> is the process of building versions of your project for different locales.\nThe localization process includes the following actions.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">提取文本以翻译成不同的语言</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Extract text for translation into different languages</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">格式化特定语言环境的数据</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Format data for a specific locale</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><em>语言环境</em>标识人们使用特定语言或语言变体的区域。可能的区域包括国家和地理区域。语言环境决定了以下详细信息的格式和解析。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <em>locale</em> identifies a region in which people speak a particular language or language variant.\nPossible regions includes countries and geographical regions.\nA locale determines the formatting and parsing of the following details.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">度量单位，包括日期和时间、数字和货币</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Measurement units including date and time, numbers, and currencies</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">翻译名称，包括时区、语言和国家</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Translated names including time zones, languages, and countries</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有关本地化和国际化的快速介绍，请观看此视频：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For a quick introduction to localization and internationalization watch this video:</p>\n\n<div class=\"video-container\">\n<iframe allow=\"accelerometer; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KNTN-nsbV7M\"></iframe>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angular-internationalization\" translation-result=\"on\">了解 Angular 国际化<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about Angular internationalization<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Common internationalization tasks\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">常见任务</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common tasks</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何实现与 Angular 国际化有关的常见任务</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement many of the common tasks associated with Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">常见国际化任务</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common internationalization tasks</p>\n    \n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Optional internationalization tasks\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">可选实践</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Optional practices</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何实现与 Angular 国际化有关的可选实践</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement optional practices associated with Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">可选国际化实践</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Optional internationalization practices</p>\n    \n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Internationalization example\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">国际化范例</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Internationalization example</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">查看一个 Angular 国际化的例子</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Review an example of Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 国际化应用范例</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Example Angular Internationalization application</p>\n    \n    </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 6/6/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/FormStyle\n - api/common/FormatWidth\n - api/common/NumberFormatStyle\n - api/common/NumberSymbol\n - api/common/Plural\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/formatDate\n - api/common/formatNumber\n - api/common/formatPercent\n - api/common/getCurrencySymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleCurrencyName\n - api/common/getLocaleCurrencySymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleDateFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleDateTimeFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleDayNames\n - api/common/getLocaleDayPeriods\n - api/common/getLocaleDirection\n - api/common/getLocaleEraNames\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/getLocaleFirstDayOfWeek\n - api/common/getLocaleId\n - api/common/getLocaleMonthNames\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberSymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleTimeFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleWeekEndRange\n - api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - guide/i18n-example\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n - guide/i18n-example\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview\n - guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\n - guide/i18n-overview#angular-国际化\n - guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\n - guide/i18n-overview#了解-angular-国际化\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"}